data.description: A beautiful and well taken care of 3 bed, 2 bath home in East Norman. An inviting arched front porch welcomes you inside to a spacious living room with a wood burning fireplace and beautiful new flooring. The kitchen boasts ample storage and a walk in pantry. The kitchen has a new dishwasher and microwave. The primary suite offers vaulted ceilings with a walk in closet. The split floor plans allows for two secondary bedrooms off the entry hall. The large backyard is great for the upcoming Spring/Summer gatherings and so much more. The home offers a brand new fence and a new roof.
